{"tid":1243296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[621] 重大行動上 別靠民陣 應靠群眾","createTime":"2019-06-19T11:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T01:38:07.000Z","uid":78873,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc296632adc4afa2ccf478e3ac54103c64968e8a","tid":1243296,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"純理性學術上既討論 <br />\n要知道 一般政黨思維 只會為延續議席為首要目的<br />\n重大行動 不要依賴他們發起<br />\n例如衝某國禮賓府 對他們來說如此激進的行動 他們是不會敢推動的  小則人命傷亡 大則某國軍隊正式入城 到時候背負的罪名 可不少.<br />\n<br />\n但運動又不能完全沒有政黨的endorsement或backup 因為只有他們與外國有connection. 有更大的號召力.<br />\n<br />\n參與野餐既人要做既 就係自發做咗先 有成果了 政黨自然痴過來搶focus<br />\n群眾才是主角 先利用政黨的是群眾  再讓政黨利用群眾"},{"pid":"ecc2c8e2a48f8adf8d8d2dac2b6acbc5cefa6c5b","tid":1243296,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7ebd8d5a91b64064ba5228586a3f23af12c8d553","tid":1243296,"uid":50762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPWPZ6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPWPZ6P.png&h=6ef9147c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBy3j6Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBy3j6Q.png&h=16ebf50e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d6ebdfb28cb93d45a8c736b4b2a002ebd3ae8","tid":1243296,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"唔敢衝但又想出一分力？請團結凝聚力量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241997\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241997</a><br />\n<br />\n新增發佈資訊平台<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fcivildefenceforcehk&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu99AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=8ff3c40f\" target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk</a><br />\nTelegram 聯絡: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKCDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft